{"tid":900841,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得梁佑嘉Abella ? 原來已經結咗婚了!","createTime":"2018-11-13T14:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T05:23:37.000Z","uid":44725,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c859577f54a4c4a3cfb5e36f08224694375489","tid":900841,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"恭喜<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/13/tjsJ7y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F13%2FtjsJ7y.png&h=8c9c6645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/13/zrUVyk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F13%2FzrUVyk.jpg&h=7a8633d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/13/wyaSto.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F13%2FwyaSto.jpg&h=47a7eddf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40da5ad6ecfe4ad98bf9e3e8461dfb5a19d84339","tid":900841,"uid":170867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"好耐了"},{"pid":"f5aae6f3655cfd66e996f32aec331868be027759","tid":900841,"uid":27064,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"王菲終結者 梁佑嘉<br />\n係Feeling Me入面, Abella 佢同時以三種語言, 五個風格, 共15個變化去演繹一首流行曲, 我可以好大膽咁講呢首比王菲既紅豆更加經典!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好話KELLY, 就算王菲永遠都做唔到梁佑嘉既爽朗, 真誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3757be239055a01994b3fd3a6565a0687faef05","tid":900841,"uid":20336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"老豆紅底種票選議員果個？<br />\n夾硬靠 daddy 泵水出垃圾碟"},{"pid":"5c646ecab53bd1ca4343f2ea4ca93ca4b9dc09f8","tid":900841,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3757be239055a01994b3fd3a6565a0687faef05","tid":900841,"uid":20336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"老豆紅底種票選議員果個？<br />\n夾硬靠 daddy 泵水出垃圾碟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:07:07.000Z","msg":"前期少少有個叫張德豪,一樣靠老豆不過唱功ok,最後老豆著咗草,另外一個就係麥浚龍,都係老豆泵水"},{"pid":"393f8eb57dbb99be3db790d3950d56f982f5e774","tid":900841,"uid":8986,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"個名好難接受, 好困擾囉...糧油加....通脹咩....而家生活已經好困難 不如直接叫 Inflation Leung 啦!<br />\n<br />\n做農民既就鐘意 &ldquo;糧油加&rdquo; 啫, 種得多賺得多嗎<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢個名邊個改啦&hellip;. 如果係屋企改, 阿爸可能真係務農 如果連老豆都唔認既就一定出人頭地. 聖保祿都係咁上下, 你睇人地幾出名丫, 仲有學校用佢命名添<br />\n<br />\n再唔係可以唱阿 Sam 個首 &ldquo;加價熱潮&rdquo; 糖又加！糧油加! 幾好聽呀, 一定掂<br />\n<br />\n其實金銀業貿易場應該邀請做吉祥物, 等D人見到就諗起通脹, 係咁買金抗通脹囉<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就去聯儲局, 日日對住伯南克, 橫掂佢咁想適度通脹, 咪滿足佢囉 不過唔好對太耐, 我驚佢受不了囉, I mean 惡性通脹呀, OK?<br />\n<br />\n唉!早日放工, 座地鐵(我呢D窮撚唔坐地鐵, 唔通馬車咩), 見到有個燈箱廣告, 有一華人女子, 雙手托下巴, do 起個嘴. 心入面都無話 &ldquo;這麼&hellip;..&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不過望一望個名&hellip;係&hellip;係....真係呀! 不禁呀左一聲 &ldquo;通脹!! 放過我啦!!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n其實, 我已經好慘, 係呢個通脹既年代, 唔好市講話二手飯都可能要食, 為左用少D錢, 唔怕老實講, 底褲都要著完前面反轉再著多一日, 點解咁做呢? 因為可以洗少一次, 用少一次水, 真係想用少D錢, 對抗通脹!<br />\n<br />\n但竟然, 放左工都要見到呢張 poster ?! Inflation Leung, 放過我啦!!!"},{"pid":"42c55675bba1ef7d5059807dedf6e283ebbaf7de","tid":900841,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"急急踩"},{"pid":"f38da5ef757b4125ceda86d89860182ca3b6720a","tid":900841,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"實在令我真不解真不解真不解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12bf0ca0b7d81e06c057a6a1ff53e22d67b76e5","tid":900841,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score